	An adapter convert the interface of a class into another interface clients expect. 
	It lets classes work together that couldn’t otherwise because of incompatible interfaces.
	
	Ever tried to use a your camera memory card in your laptop. 
	You cannot use it directly simply because there is no port in laptop which accept it. 
	You must use a compatible card reader. 
	You put your memory card into the card reader and then inject the card reader into the laptop. 
	This card reader can be called the adapter.